<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-cn">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, user-scalable=no">
  <meta name="renderer" content="webkit" />
  <title>丹露网供应金融链</title>
  {include './part/addCss.tpl'}
</head>
<body>
	<div class="main clearfix">
		<div class="title">
			<h2>有没有让生意更容易的方法？</h2>
		</div>
		<div class="danlu-supply-chain">
			<div class="sub-title">
				<h1>丹露网金融供应链</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="sub-content">
				<h3>丹露网供应链金融，是针对酒饮产业的业务特点和实际需求而设计的一系列供应链金融服务，致力于为丹露平台上的厂商用户、配送商用户和终端店用户提供覆盖业务全过程的金融服务。</h3>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="enterprise-loans">
			<div class="el-sub-title">
				<h1>核心企业贷</h1>
				<h3>丹露网供应链金融首款产品</h3>
			</div>
			<div class="el-sub-content">
				<h3>核心企业贷是丹露网联手海尔云贷为丹露网核心经销商打造的金融产品，产品不仅致力于为经销商解决投资贸易中的资金问题，同时也为经销商的下游分销商、终端店解决贸易中的融资问题。以经销商为核心企业，服务好产业链上下游环节。</h3>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="enterprise-loans-step">
			<div class="el-sub-title">
				<h1>1</h1>
				<h1 style="color:#666;font-size">核心企业贷模式</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="el-sub-content" style="width:732px;">
				<img src="../resource/images/supplychain/bkg-0.png">
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="enterprise-loans-step">
			<div class="el-sub-title">
				<h1>2</h1>
				<h1 style="color:#666;font-size">核心企业贷优势</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="el-sub-content">
				<img src="../resource/images/supplychain/bkg-1.png">
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="enterprise-loans-step">
			<div class="el-sub-title">
				<h1>3</h1>
				<h1 style="color:#666;font-size">核心企业贷详情</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="el-sub-content">
				<img src="../resource/images/supplychain/bkg-2.png">
				<div class="step-content" style="width:360px;">
					<h2 style="font-weight:bold;">适用对象：</h2>
					<h2>丹露网经销商用户</h2>
					<h2  style="font-weight:bold;margin-top:16px;">贷款用途：</h2>
					<h2>经销商向厂家进行采购；</h2>
					<h2>经销商推荐分销商、终端店向经销商采购</h2>
				</div>
				<img src="../resource/images/supplychain/bkg-3.png">
				<div class="step-content" style="width:124px;">
					<h2 style="font-weight:bold;">产品类型：</h2>
					<h2>纯授信、无抵押、不控货</h2>
					<h2  style="font-weight:bold;margin-top:16px;">额度：</h2>
					<h2>3000万</h2>
				</div>
				<img src="../resource/images/supplychain/bkg-4.png">
				<div class="step-content" style="width:120px;">
					<h2 style="font-weight:bold;">贷款利息：</h2>
					<h2>年息12%</h2>
					<h2  style="font-weight:bold;margin-top:16px;">授信期限：</h2>
					<h2>12个月</h2>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="enterprise-loans-step">
			<div class="el-sub-title" style="width:300px;">
				<h1>4</h1>
				<h1 style="color:#666;font-size">核心企业贷申请条件及流程</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="el-sub-content">
				<img src="../resource/images/supplychain/bkg-5.png">
				<div class="step-content" style="width:318x;">
					<img src="../resource/images/supplychain/step-content.png">
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="contact-us">
			<img src="../resource/images/supplychain/contact.png">
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>